Data.jsonData: {"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"What am I doing at the beach?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"He was talking about another world... But I don’t feel like I’ve left Mexico."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"Take that! And give me your wallet, loser."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"A robbery in broad daylight...? Yeah, I’m still in Mexico."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"…Huh?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"People of your race disgust me..."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"But stop! I didn’t do anything."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"It’s not every day you come across a cowboy attacking an egg, but if there’s racism, I’m on Earth."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"We should lock people like you in the cake."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"The cake??"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"Not so fast half-pint. I hope you’re not here to defend this... This species of... This filthy..."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Really? You’re going to say that kind of thing in the year 20-<skipLine>"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"BALDY?!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"...Baldy?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"Dude…"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/EyrCott/po_eyrcott_bald_1","talkerName":"Eyr Cott","line":"Thanks for the money, scum. I invite you to try and get it back if you can."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"WAIT, YOU TALKED ABOUT A CAKE!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Damn. How is a cowboy this fast."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"Thanks for trying to help me... But don’t worry, this happens to me every day."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Yeah, yeah… He talked about a cake. Do you know what he’s talking about?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"The cake? Well yeah, everyone knows about it. You’re not from around here?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Not really. What country are we in?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"Sucredorge."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Where’s that? In the United States?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"The United States?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"…Oh shit... I’m really in another world."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"Uh… I’m not sure what you’re talking about, but if you’re looking for the cake, I can take you there."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Really?!"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"On one condition. Help me get revenge on that cowboy bastard."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Fine, OK… But it better be quick. I’m starving."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"What’s your name, by the way?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Jimi, and you?"}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Yankee/po_yankee_neutral_1","talkerName":"Yankee","line":"So… I’m Yankee."}
{"portraitPath":"Portraits/Jimi/po_jimi_neutral_1", "talkerName":"Jimi","line":"Great, let’s go."}
